by CanuckleheadCowgirl, magnetocerebro, Ophelia_L, silmarilz1701

In this final installment of the 867 universe, our heroes are trying to adjust to life after the war. Hydra has been defeated, and so has the Capitol, so they’re all looking forward to retirement.

Of course, nothing is ever that easy.

When it comes time for Marvel to choose its next leader, the election doesn’t go quite as planned. After all, when you have Norman Osborn running for power, he’s not going to leave anything to chance.

So our heroes must come out of their well-earned retirement to take down one last would-be dictator… or risk losing everything they worked so hard to achieve.

summary: This has been stuck in my mind since Infinity War.
body:
This has been stuck in my mind since Infinity War.

With half of the earth Dusted what the fuck happens to people who were pregnant? What happens when they got dusted? Does the fucking fetus or Embryo just get dusted with them? Since their technically two separate people does only the mother get dusted? Does the fucking baby just kinda appear with the placenta still connected to it? What if it’s in the first few months? After the mother gets dusted does just some random red blob appear? Will someone notice that some random person just got dusted & some red blob appeared or if second or third trimester will the fucking baby just appear crying & shit. Do you take it to the hospital? Are nurseries just fucking packed because so many fucking babies were all born prematurely? What is the fucking fetus or baby or whatever Dusted inside the mother? Does the mother just run inside a plan parenthood or hospital yelling “DUST IS COMING OUT OF MY VAGINA!” Is it considered An Abortion if the baby just got fucking dustes inside? & what happens when things go back to normal or something that brings everyone who got dusted back? Does the baby just go back inside the mother? What if she’s pregnant again & all of a sudden her missing child just appeared back inside with it’s sibling?

OUT OF ALL THE QUESTIONS I HAVE FOR AVENGERS 4 THIS IS THE ONE I WANT TO KNOW!
